TrueTileMon is a lightweight, tile-style system monitor designed for seamless integration with the Windows taskbar. Inspired by TrueLaunchBar aesthetics, it displays real-time CPU usage per core, RAM stats, battery status, and more ‚Äî all in a compact, customizable UI. Ideal for users who want instant system feedback without clutter.

